description: Did you hear the news during Minecraft LIVE? Dragon Ball Z powers into Minecraft later this year! Want to get ready early? Claim your free Super Saiyan Hair in the Marketplace and start charging up.
title: Minecraft x Dragon Ball Z Tease

author: Minecraft
description:
YES indeed – Dragon Ball is coming to Minecraft! Play as fighters like Goku, Vegeta, and Trunks. Battle in destructible arenas from the series, including the Cell Games and World Martial Arts Tournament. Each character brings their own moves, cinematic ultimates, and custom VFX. From co-op tournaments to wild 5v5 brawls, Minecraft’s power level is about to be over MINE-THOUSAND! Take your blocky battles Super Saiyan!
